DESCRIPTION:Registration required.&#13\;\n&#13\;\nThis event is open to a
 ll.&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​Curious about building with Claude but not sure wher
 e to start?&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​Join us for a hands-on Claude Code Workshop 
 led by Todd Greco\, designed for beginners\, builders\, and anyone curio
 us about using Claude inside a real coding environment.&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​
 This session will walk through how to set up the Claude Code CLI and dev
 elopment environment\, and how Claude can assist with everyday coding ta
 sks like debugging\, file manipulation\, and feature building.&#13\;\n&#
 13\;\n​Claude Code allows developers to run Claude directly in the termi
 nal\, making it a powerful companion for building software\, experimenti
 ng with ideas\, and accelerating projects.&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​After the wor
 kshop\, participants are welcome to stay\, experiment\, and work on idea
 s together in an open build session.&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​Whether you’re a de
 veloper\, hacker\, or simply curious about how AI can support your workf
 low\, this session will help you get started.&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​What you'l
 l learn&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​How to set up the Claude Code CLI&#13\;\n&#13\;\
 n​How to authenticate and connect your Claude account&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​Us
 ing Claude inside your terminal development workflow&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​Pra
 ctical ways Claude can assist with coding tasks&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​Tips for
  experimenting and building with Claude&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​Requirements&#13
 \;\n&#13\;\n​Participants should have:&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​A laptop&#13\;\n&
 #13\;\n​A Claude account (Claude Pro recommended)&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​Basic 
 familiarity with using a terminal&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​Note: Claude Pro provi
 des access to the Claude app and Claude Code. API access is separate and
  billed based on usage.&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​Schedule&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​10:00 A
 M – 11:00 AM&#13\;\nClaude Code Setup Workshop with Todd Greco&#13\;\n&#
 13\;\n​11:00 AM – 1:00 PM&#13\;\nOpen build session — experiment\, colla
 borate\, and work on ideas.&#13\;\n&#13\;\n​Come learn something new\, b
 uild something interesting\, and meet others exploring the Claude ecosys
 tem in Portland.&#13\;\n\n\nTags: AI\, Claude\, Anthropic\n\nImported fr
 om: http://calagator.org/events/1250482509
URL:https://luma.com/workshopwithToddGreco
SUMMARY:Claude Code workshop
LOCATION:PSU - Metro Innovation Hub - 2130 SW 5th Ave.\, PDX\, OR 97201: 
 false
SEQUENCE:1
