 n side projects\, online courses\, or even your day-to-day work tasks.&#
 13\;\nStill uncertain? Let's chat on Discord!&#13\;\n## Venue:&#13\;\nTh
 e Venue is at Capital One Café\, who is graciously allowing us to host a
