DESCRIPTION:This one-hour tour of the [Portland Art Museum](https://portl
 andartmuseum.org/) will include a tour of accessibility features\, follo
 wed by an exploration of the museum's tactile graphics.&#13\;\n&#13\;\nT
 he studio has been reserved - so we will have a quiet place to talk and 
 explore the tactiles. Personal belongings can be left in this area durin
 g the tour\, as the studio will be securely locked.&#13\;\n&#13\;\n**Thi
 s tour is being offered free of charge\, but an RSVP is required.** Once
  the tour is completed\, food and beverages can be purchased at Coquelic
 o within the Portland Art Museum. Attendees can continue to tour the mus
 eum if they wish.&#13\;\n&#13\;\n**Museum Staff Request:** Please avoid 
 wearing scented body and laundry products\, as well as essential oils.&#
 13\;\n&#13\;\n**Accessibility Request:** The Portland Art Museum (PAM) n
 ow has elevators and an accessible entrance. Here are further details on
  the [PAM's accessibility offerings](https://portlandartmuseum.org/acces
 sibility/). Please let us know if you have any accommodation requests\, 
 such as stools\, etc.&#13\;\n&#13\;\n**Where to Meet:** The lobby\, more
  details to come. Please look for our logo.\n\nTags: User Research\, a11
 y\, accessibility\, accessibility lawsuits\, accessible technology\, acc
 essible web design\, disability\, human rights\, inclusive design\, meet
 up:event=313739561\, meetup:group=Portland-Accessibility-and-User-Experi
 ence-Meetup\, mobile user experience\, screen reader\, structured negoti
 ation\, technology\, universal design\, usability\, user experience\, wc
 ag\, web accessibility\, web design\, art\, museum\n\nImported from: htt
 p://calagator.org/events/1250482503
URL:https://pdxa11yux.org/events/2026/03/22/portland-art-museum-accessibi
 lity-tour.html
SUMMARY:Portland Accessibility and User Experience Meetup (PDX A11Y UX) -
  Portland Art Museum Accessibility Tour
LOCATION:Portland Art Museum: 1219 SW Park Avenue\, Portland Oregon 97205
  US
SEQUENCE:1
END:VEVENT
