 and Thursdays) focused on imagining and making better futures.&#13\;\n&#
 13\;\nImagine an artist community\, a think tank\, and a research center
  in the same building. People in all of those fields working alongside e
 ach other imagining and creating different futures together. Cross polli
 nation and inspiration. Liberal Arts and STEM and R&amp\;D. Photographer
 s\, physicists\, authors\, astronomers\, musicians\, makers\, mathematic
 ians\, designers\, developers\, fashionistas\, climatologists and all ma
 nner of imaginative optimists.&#13\;\n&#13\;\nAll Better Futures Club ev
 ents are covered by the Contributor Covenant Code of Conduct (https://ww
 w.contributor-covenant.org)\n\nTags: ruby\, STEM\, liberal arts\, commun
 ity\, hacking\, AI\n\nImported from: http://calagator.org/events/1250482
